---
title: Spiced Salmon & Creamy Herb Sauce with Parmesan Mash & Zesty Veggies
description: It’s hard to beat this classic combination of salmon, dill and mash. But tonight, we’ve added some extra-special touches (like
adding Parmesan to the mash or infusing dill and chives into a creamy sauce) to turn your ordinary bistro-style dinner into something extraordinary!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/spiced-salmon-creamy-herb-sauce-50faf3fd.jpg
